	<ThingDef ParentName="MorrowRim_Dunmer_ArmourMakeable_Chitin">
		<defName>MorrowRim_Dunmer_ArmourHelmet_ChitinWatchman</defName>
		<label>Redoran watchman helmet</label>
		<description>A large chitin helmet, made from the shell of an arthropod encountered only in Redoran controlled land. Designed to provide a good range of long-distance vision, whilst still offering reasonable protection. This comes at the cost of short-distance vision, forcing wearers to walk slightly more carefully than normal, lest they trip over trama root.\n\nTypically worn by Redoran guards that are proficient with bonemold long bows.</description>
